Code Ocean for publishing your reproducible Jupyter Notebooks

Seth Green

November 13, 2018

Code Ocean

  • Code Ocean is, more or less:
  • JupyterLab IDE + modifications
  • A robust dependency management system
  • A publishing platform (DOIs & stable URLs)
  • A sharing platform (embed your compute capsules on webpages)

An option for publishing your Jupyter Notebooks reproducibly

  • use NBconvert
  • install all Packages at outset
  • get a nice Dockerfile when youre done

Reproducible Mode

Notebook + environment + nbconvert = a rendered HTML
